activities:
Rowan Companies, Inc. will use and otherwise process European Employee Data in the United States for the following purposes:

   -Workflow management, such as assigning, managing, and administering projects; 
   -Compensation, including stock plan administration and compensation analysis; 
   -Payroll processing; 
   -Performance management; 
   -Succession planning; 
   -Benefits and personnel administration; 
   -IT helpdesk and support services; 
   -Monitoring and enforcing compliance with company policies and procedures; and 
   -Employee taxes, accounting and project cost allocation, recruiting, safety and incident reporting, other industry reporting requirements, employee travel coordination, corporate credit cards for employees, employee training, employee length of service rewards and audit requirements.
